### Get all series
GET http://localhost:3000/series
Accept: application/json

###

### Get series by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/series/68d24bc40706a8ca2a62d5f3
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new series
POST http://localhost:3000/series
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Breaking Bad",
  "genre": "Drama, Crime, Thriller",
  "seasons": 5,
  "episodes": 62,
  "description": "A high school chemistry teacher turns to a life of crime after being diagnosed with cancer.",
  "releaseYear": 2008,
  "available": true
}

###

### Update an existing series
PUT http://localhost:3000/series/68d24bf10706a8ca2a62d604
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Breaking Bad (Remastered)",
  "genre": "Drama, Crime, Thriller",
  "seasons": 5,
  "episodes": 63,
  "description": "Remastered edition with improved visual effects and one new episode.",
  "releaseYear": 2008,
  "available": true
}

###

### Delete a series
DELETE http://localhost:3000/series/68d24bc40706a8ca2a62d5f3
Accept: application/json
